              © 2024 U卡评测. 保留所有权利.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-6 mt-4 md:mt-0">
              <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">友情链接:</span>
              <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-sm transition-colors">币安</a>
              <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-sm transition-colors">欧易</a>
